Makefile:83: recipe for target 'all' failed
gmake: *** [all] Error 2
```

I looked into https://stackoverflow.com/questions/10851247/how-to-activate-c-11-in-cmake and https://stackoverflow.com/questions/33394934/converting-std-cxx11string-to-stdstring but none worked.

